export const getOrder = /* GraphQL */ `
  query GetOrder($id: ID!) {
    getOrder(id: $id) {
      id
      orderNo
      customer
      saleDate
      createdAt
      user
      updatedAt
      _version
      _deleted
      _lastChangedAt
    }
  }
`;

  query ListOrders(
    $id: ID
    $filter: ModelOrderFilterInput
    $limit: Int
    $nextToken: String
    $sortDirection: ModelSortDirection
  ) {
    listOrders(
      id: $id
      filter: $filter
      limit: $limit
      nextToken: $nextToken
      sortDirection: $sortDirection

        customer

`;
